{"pagelen": 50, "values": [{"update": {"description": "I am considering the following use cases:\r\n\r\n1. Catkin workspaces installations (currently broken for the need of root perms to install /usr/share/drcsim/setup.sh)\r\n1.  System from source installations\r\n1.  Deb package generation\r\n\r\nIn 2 and 3 we want to keep setup.sh into /usr/share/drcsim/setup.sh while in 1 we don't want it at all. Another way to control this would be to introduce a building parameter to install it or not, but then magic won't happen anymore automatically for all cases.\r\n\r\n@gerkey do you see any flaw to this hack besides it is just this, a hack?", "title": "Install setup.sh in /usr only if PREFIX is /opt/ros in order to respect catkin ws", "destination": {"commit": {"hash": "bdc9126aa479", "type": "commit", "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/drcsim/commit/bdc9126aa479.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/drcsim/commits/bdc9126aa479"}}}, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/drcsim.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/drcsim"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{247b5408-ae91-4e3c-b2f9-a21994658d11}ts=c_plus_plus"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "drcsim", "full_name": "osrf/drcsim", "uuid": "{247b5408-ae91-4e3c-b2f9-a21994658d11}"}, "branch": {"name": "default"}}, "reason": "", "source": {"commit": {"hash": "8fbdfba95ef1", "type": "commit", "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/drcsim/commit/8fbdfba95ef1.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/drcsim/commits/8fbdfba95ef1"}}}, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/drcsim.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/drcsim"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{247b5408-ae91-4e3c-b2f9-a21994658d11}ts=c_plus_plus"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "drcsim", "full_name": "osrf/drcsim", "uuid": "{247b5408-ae91-4e3c-b2f9-a21994658d11}"}, "branch": {"name": "fix_catkinws_installations"}}, "state": "MERGED", "author": {"display_name": "Jose Luis Ri