tall setup.sh in /usr only if PREFIX is /opt/ros in order to respect catkin ws"}, "content": {"raw": "Two comments:\n\n* Currently the setup.sh script is installed to: `share/drcsim_model_resources/drcsim_model_resources/setup.sh`. Perhaps we can remove one of those `drcsim_model_resources/` from the path?\n\n* Can we also install the setup.sh to `${CMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX}/share/drcsim` for catkin workspaces?", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>Two comments:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Currently the setup.sh script is installed to: <code>share/drcsim_model_resources/drcsim_model_resources/setup.sh</code>. Perhaps we can remove one of those <code>drcsim_model_resources/</code> from the path?</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Can we also install the setup.sh to <code>${CMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX}/share/drcsim</code> for catkin workspaces?</p>\n</li>\n</ul>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2013-09-27T21:08:27.686897+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Steve Peters", "uuid": "{2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1fb4816dad9e68337d3096f750951f6cd=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.netinitialsSP-1.png"}}, "nickname": "Steven Peters", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:5de38267-b118-494c-aa76-4fab35448816"}, "updated_on": "2013-09-27T21:08:27.694329+00:00", "type": "pullrequest_comment", "id": 617468}, "pull_request": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 388, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/drcsim/pullrequests/388.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/drcsim/pull-requests/388"}}, "title": "Install setup.sh in /usr only if PREFIX is /opt/ros in order to respect catkin ws"}}, {"update": {"description": "I am considering the following use cases:\r\n\r\n1. Catkin workspaces installations (currently broken for the need of root perms to install /usr/share/drcsim/setup.sh)\r\n1.  System from source installations\r\n1.  Deb package generation\r\n\r\nIn 2 and 3 we want to keep setup.sh into /usr/share/drcsim/setup.sh while in 1 we don't want it at all. Another way to control this would be to introduce a building parameter to install it or not, but then magic won't happen anymore automatically for all cases.\r\n\r\n@gerkey do you see any flaw to this hack besides it is just this, a hack?", "title": "Install setup.sh in /usr only if PREFIX is /opt/ros in order to respect catkin ws", "destination": {"commit": {"hash": "bdc9126aa479", "type": "commit", "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/drcsim/commit/bdc9126aa479.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/drcsim/commits/bdc9126aa479"}}}, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/drcsim.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/drcsim"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{247b5408-ae91-4e3c-b2f9-a21994658d11}ts=c_plus_plus"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "drcsim", "full_name": "osrf/drcsim", "uuid": "{247b5408-ae91-4e3c-b2f9-a21994658d11}"}, "branch": {"name": "default"}}, "reason": "", "source": {"commit": {"hash": "420d90f67fe5", "type": "commit", "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/drcsim/commit/420d90f67fe5.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/drcsim/commits/420d90f67fe5"}}}, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/drcsim.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/drcsim"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{247b5408-ae91-4e3c-b2f9-a21994658d11}ts=c_plus_plus"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "drcsim", "full_name": "osrf/drcsim", "uuid": "{247b5408-ae91-4e3c-b2f9-a21994658d11}"}, "branch": {"name": "fix_catkinws_installations"}}, "state": "OPEN", "author": {"display_name": "Jose Luis Rivero", "uuid": "{d12309b2-f745-42ee-b119-aec4fcdf81fe}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7Bd12309b2-f745-42ee-b119-aec4fcdf81fe%7D"}, "h